title: Parish of Doonside
text:
The parish of Doonside is an <a href="Australian">Australian</a> <a href="cadastre">cadastral</a> <a href="Parish%20%28administrative%20division%29">parish</a> in the <a href="New%20South%20Wales">NSW</a> <a href="Lands%20administrative%20divisions%20of%20New%20South%20Wales">county</a> of <a href="Narromine%20County">Narromine</a>. It is located approximately midway between <a href="Tottenham%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Tottenham</a> and <a href="Narromine">Narromine</a> and is in Narromine <a href="Shire">Shire</a>.
The parish should not be confused with the <a href="Western%20Sydney">western</a> <a href="Sydney">Sydney</a> <a href="suburb">suburb</a> of <a href="Doonside%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Doonside</a>.
Approx
